      little left for a horse to mount my doll on; and I wasn't going to get a
      screw, so I went to Papa, and he gave me five shillings. And, oh, do you
      know, Rose can't bear me to be with you. Jealousy, I suppose, for you're
      very agreeable. And, do you know, your Mama is coming to-day? I've got a
